          <span class="font-bold text-white">on</span> the org instead of integrated
          <span class="font-bold text-white">into</span> it.
        </p>
        <div class="mx-auto mt-7 h-px w-16 bg-red-200/35"></div>
        <p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-xl text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold italic leading-relaxed text-white">
          Your clients are sitting in that 95% &mdash; unless you change the layer.
        </p>
